			title: "Story Continue"
			x: 0.0d
			y: -1.0d
		}
		{
			dependencies: ["5DBF17299A0DE31E"]
			description: [
				"&6&oThe first signs came from the remnants of ancient power. Something in the deep was roused, and what should have stayed buried now moves again beneath the stone. When it falls, it should leave more than silence behind.&r&r"
				""
				"&4&o\"Old ruins do not stay buried forever, and neither do their treasures.\"&r&r"
			]
			icon: "cataclysm:desert_eye"
			id: "7E2ECADBF5753E0B"
			rewards: [
