		{
			dependencies: ["5FB3D665CD41869F"]
			description: [
				"&6&oThe signs are no longer just beasts, but messengers. A harbinger has appeared, as if the corruption itself has learned how to warn us before the next strike.&r&r"
				""
				"&4&o\"It is not just coming. It is announcing itself.\"&r&r"
