			description: [
				"&6&oFrom the ruins came a curse that still clings to the living world. Its influence warps those who come too close, leaving behind only twisted purpose and broken memory.&r&r"
				""
				"&4&o\"The ruins are not empty. They are watching.\"&r&r"
