			description: [
				"&6&oThe path ahead leads through ash and oath. Whatever guards this place was forged for war, and it will not yield without being broken.&r&r"
				""
				"&4&o\"Steel, flame, and broken vows. That is all the underworld seems to keep now.\"&r&r"
