			dependencies: ["1680504501FCFF80"]
			description: [
				"&o&6The miasma has not been destroyed, only driven back. Yet the trail is clearer now: a chain of corrupted relics, broken rulers, and old powers has pointed to a final gate beyond the worlds we know. Something watches from there, patient and silent, waiting for the next step.&r&r"
				""
				"&4&o\"This was only the middle of the road. The end is still ahead.\"&r&r"
